263
00:15:33,483 --> 00:15:35,118
That's the end of it.

264
00:15:36,947 --> 00:15:38,288
Howard?

265
00:15:38,313 --> 00:15:40,587
- That's the end.
- Mm.

266
00:15:40,626 --> 00:15:41,954
- [Tape recorder clicks]
- [Dog barks in distance]

267
00:15:41,979 --> 00:15:43,337
Could you...?

268
00:15:44,290 --> 00:15:46,190
Oh, yeah.

269
00:15:49,536 --> 00:15:52,251
Well, now do you believe me?

270
00:15:55,149 --> 00:15:57,435
I don't even know where to begin.

271
00:15:58,289 --> 00:16:00,548
