272
00:16:00,835 --> 00:16:04,134
Your brother is one
world-class son of a bitch.

273
00:16:05,228 --> 00:16:06,527
No offense.

274
00:16:07,630 --> 00:16:10,501
I just... I really wish you'd told me

275
00:16:10,526 --> 00:16:12,946
