attack that you nearly gave me.

280
00:16:23,493 --> 00:16:25,468
Chuck, this tape...

281
00:16:25,493 --> 00:16:28,215
I'm not sure exactly
what it accomplishes.

282
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:30,708
Look, you know evidentiary
rules better than I do,

283
00:16:30,744 --> 00:16:32,544
but a secretly recorded tape

284
00:16:32,569 --> 00:16:34,622
with a problematic chain of evidence?

285
00:16:34,657 --> 00:16:36,501
You're gonna have a helluva
time getting that admitted.

286
00:16:36,526 --> 00:16:37,719
I agree.

287
00:16:37,744 --> 00:16:39,524
And if you somehow put
it in front of a jury,

288
00:16:39,549 --> 00:16:40,981
Jimmy'd call a dozen audio experts,

289
00:16:41,006 --> 00:16:42,305
