to look forward to.

399
00:27:21,619 --> 00:27:22,937
- [Chuckling] Okay.
- Okay, bye-bye.

400
00:27:22,962 --> 00:27:24,446
- Bye!
- See ya!

401
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,053
