402
00:27:27,078 --> 00:27:29,199
Uh, thank you for waiting so patiently.

403
00:27:29,234 --> 00:27:31,234
Who do we have next?

404
00:27:33,134 --> 00:27:34,655
[Sighs]

405
00:27:34,800 --> 00:27:36,476
That'd be me.

406
00:27:41,920 --> 00:27:43,403
Hello, hello.

407
00:27:43,428 --> 00:27:45,708
It's so good to see you again.

408
00:27:45,733 --> 00:27:49,803
I escorted you and your
clients onto my base.

409
00:27:50,256 --> 00:27:52,614
I treated you with
hospitality and respect,

410
00:27:52,639 --> 00:27:53,823
and now I come to find

411
00:27:53,859 --> 00:27:55,659
every word out of your
mouth is a damn lie.

412
00:27:55,684 --> 00:27:58,428
Captain, please. Why don't...
Sit down. Take a load off.

413
00:27:58,455 --> 00:28:01,342
Hey, I'll get you a complimentary
coffee or a soft drink?

414
00:28:01,375 --> 00:28:04,334
And your so-called war
hero, "Fudge" Talbott?

415
00:28:04,359 --> 00:28:06,106
No such person... never was.

416
00:28:06,131 --> 00:28:09,395
Granted, some artistic
license may have been taken.

417
00:28:09,420 --> 00:28:11,271
You entered government property
under false pretenses, sir.

418
00:28:11,296 --> 00:28:13,780
Whoa, whoa. I am no
expert on your procedures

419
00:28:13,805 --> 00:28:15,108
and your protocols and whatnot,

420
00:28:15,133 --> 00:28:18,111
so if... if we failed to
cross a "t" or dot an "i,"

421
00:28:18,136 --> 00:28:20,608
I sincerely apologize
for any misunderstanding.

422
00:28:20,633 --> 00:28:21,827
N-no, no, no, it's
not a misunderstanding!

423
00:28:21,852 --> 00:28:23,600
Just step back! B-big
picture this, okay?!

424
00:28:23,625 --> 00:28:24,983
- It...
- What damage was done?!

425
00:28:25,008 --> 00:28:26,509
Hey, who was hurt, huh?

426
00:28:26,544 --> 00:28:27,795
What was damaged?

427
00:28:27,820 --> 00:28:29,148
The... the base is still there, right?

428
00:28:29,173 --> 00:28:30,773
The B-52 is, I presume, still...

429
00:28:30,798 --> 00:28:32,706
- B-29.
- Huh?

430
00:28:32,781 --> 00:28:35,451
B-29. FIFI's a B-29.

431
00:28:36,139 --> 00:28:37,703
[Chuckling] I don't...

432
00:28:37,922 --> 00:28:40,690
Oh, this is all just
one big joke to you, huh?

433
00:28:41,468 --> 00:28:43,601
- You don't like the commercial.
- No, no, I don't,

434
00:28:43,626 --> 00:28:45,025
but this has nothing
to do with the comm...

435
00:28:45,050 --> 00:28:46,616
Well, constructive
criticism is always welcome.

436
00:28:46,641 --> 00:28:48,039
- But I didn't...
- But you should realize...

437
00:28:48,064 --> 00:28:49,937
... that most people
find it uplifting...

438
00:28:49,985 --> 00:28:51,045
- ... patriotic, even.
- No.

439
00:28:51,070 --> 00:28:52,523
- You check your recruiting numbers.
- I-I-I...

440
00:28:52,548 --> 00:28:54,682
I think you're gonna see an
uptick, and you know what?

441
00:28:54,707 --> 00:28:56,807
If it turns out that Fudge
wasn't actually in the war...

442
00:28:56,832 --> 00:28:59,304
Fudge is not a person.
He wasn't in the war.

443
00:28:59,329 --> 00:29:00,943
Well, neither was Tom Cruise,

444
00:29:00,979 --> 00:29:03,258
and look what "Top Gun" did for you.

445
00:29:03,804 --> 00:29:06,648
You lied to me, you lied to my face,

446
00:29:06,673 --> 00:29:08,484
and I can't let you get away with it.

447
00:29:08,520 --> 00:29:10,045
I-I think we just...

448
00:29:10,070 --> 00:29:11,828
we're just gonna have
to agree to disagree,

449
00:29:11,853 --> 00:29:14,390
so, uh, can I get you
that coffee to go or...?

450
00:29:14,415 --> 00:29:17,920
No, no. I-I'm gonna tell
you what's happening now.

451
00:29:17,945 --> 00:29:19,836
You're gonna take that ad off the air.

452
00:29:19,861 --> 00:29:21,238
And if you play that ad one more time,

453
00:29:21,263 --> 00:29:22,861
I'm gonna go to the Judge Advocate,

454
00:29:22,886 --> 00:29:24,260
and we will take you down...

455
00:29:24,322 --> 00:29:25,989
trespassing, false representation,

456
00:29:26,024 --> 00:29:27,824
stolen valor... the whole nine yards.

457
00:29:27,859 --> 00:29:29,960
Seriously, for eight
seconds of a TV commercial?

458
00:29:29,985 --> 00:29:33,390
You take that ad down, or
there'll be hell to pay.

459
00:29:33,961 --> 00:29:35,811
That clear enough for you?

460
00:29:37,788 --> 00:29:39,444
Make me.

461
00:29:39,593 --> 00:29:41,264
- Yeah?
- [Chuckling] Yeah.

462
00:29:41,289 --> 00:29:42,577
- Make you?
- Yeah, let's do this.

463
00:29:42,602 --> 00:29:44,007
You bring your commander down here,

464
00:29:44,032 --> 00:29:46,101
and I'll explain to him
how you let us on the base,

465
00:29:46,126 --> 00:29:47,140
