- [Scoffs]

515
00:33:45,474 --> 00:33:47,174
What do I look like... RadioShack?

516
00:33:47,199 --> 00:33:50,389
It's gonna cost you whatever
it costs me, plus my end.

517
00:33:50,425 --> 00:33:52,104
Well, let's start with that.

518
00:33:52,129 --> 00:33:55,394
